    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR. This specimen retains its original 4G63 power plant, featuring MIVEC variable valve timing and a pristine twin-scroll TD05HR turbocharger. The drivetrain remains factory-spec, utilizing the Active Center Differential (ACD) and front/rear mechanical limited-slip differentials for unparalleled torque vectoring. Handling is anchored by the original MR-specific Bilstein monotube dampers and forged BBS alloy wheels, ensuring optimal unsprung weight and damping response. The Brembo braking system remains sharp with no signs of thermal glazing. This is a collector-grade example with an impeccable service history, free of any aftermarket ECU mapping or structural modifications.",
      "price": 46500.0,
