      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of a meticulously maintained vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This car has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow during my ownership. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep, original luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; a professional ceramic coating was applied last season to ensure lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, featuring supple leather seats with absolutely no bolster wear and a dashboard free of any UV damage or cracking. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized specialists. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of corrosion or fluid leaks. This sale includes two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and the factory window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
